cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.ED, cs.CV 

The paper deals with a machine learning model for personalized education, specifically knowledge tracing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of recurrent neural networks, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The regularization terms introduced in the paper are related to loss functions, which is a common topic in cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the application of the model in education, which falls under cs.ED (Education). Finally, the paper mentions the use of deep learning for image recognition, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
